_sText:
This is the first map I've ever submitted.
It took me about a week to finish all of it.
It's meant to be a gungame map.

I'm sure I could do a better job, but I as just so eager to release my 1st map so.. there you go lol :P

Use the barrels to your advantage (and also some amusing results lol)

Leave your thoughts, and some constructive criticism please (if you see any problems)
